- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on task-oriented dialog systems and language understanding. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a hybrid algorithm that combines reinforcement learning and supervised learning. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses Deep Recurrent Q-Networks (DRQN) for learning policies. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is possible as the paper discusses interfacing with a relational database. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is also possible as the paper involves managing and tracking dialog state using a database.
